00:51:04,144 --> 00:51:06,244
<font color=#FFFF00>Hannah.</font>

728
00:51:07,054 --> 00:51:08,284
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa kau begini?</font>

729
00:51:08,284 --> 00:51:09,383
<font color=#FFFF00>Minggir.</font>

730
00:51:12,054 --> 00:51:14,224
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak mengandung anakmu lagi,</font>

731
00:51:15,023 --> 00:51:16,394
<font color=#FFFF00>jadi aku tak perlu menemuimu lagi.</font>

732
00:51:16,394 --> 00:51:17,394
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

733
00:51:17,624 --> 00:51:19,063
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pikir...</font>

734
00:51:19,693 --> 00:51:21,093
<font color=#FFFF00>aku mau menikah...</font>

735
00:51:21,093 --> 00:51:23,463
<font color=#FFFF00>dengan pria miskin tanpa masa depan...</font>

736
00:51:23,664 --> 00:51:25,434
<font color=#FFFF00>yang selalu memukulku?</font>

737
00:51:28,133 --> 00:51:30,074
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku lebih baik mati sendiri...</font>

738
00:51:30,074 --> 00:51:32,704
<font color=#FFFF00>daripada membesarkan anak yang mirip denganmu.</font>

739
00:51:33,443 --> 00:51:34,474
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan coba-coba...</font>

740
00:51:35,744 --> 00:51:37,644
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau sentuh aku lagi!</font>

741
00:51:50,224 --> 00:51:51,224
<font color=#FFFF00>Lepas!</font>

742
00:51:58,503 --> 00:51:59,863
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik, bunuh aku.</font>

743
00:51:59,934 --> 00:52:01,104
<font color=#FFFF00>Bunuh aku!</font>

744
00:52:01,104 --> 00:52:03,503
<font color=#FFFF00>- Bunuh saja aku!
- Apa yang kau lakukan?</font>

745
00:52:03,503 --> 00:52:04,673
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey!</font>

746
00:52:12,043 --> 00:52:13,684
<font color=#FFFF00>Kim Hyung Soo, Ha Seon Woo.</font>

747
00:52:14,383 --> 00:52:16,084
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau di mana?</font>

748
00:52:50,954 --> 00:52:52,184
<font color=#FFFF00>Ke mana dia kira-kira?</font>

749
00:52:53,954 --> 00:52:54,954
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

750
00:52:55,593 --> 00:52:57,994
<font color=#FFFF00>Coba periksa apa Kim Hyung Soo dan Hannah...</font>

751
00:52:57,994 --> 00:53:00,894
<font color=#FFFF00>punya rumah bersama yang terdaftar dulu.</font>

752
00:53:00,894 --> 00:53:02,664
<font color=#FFFF00>Setelah itu, lacak kendaraan di dekatnya.</font>

753
00:53:02,894 --> 00:53:03,903
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay.</font>

754
00:53:11,843 --> 00:53:14,313
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku menemukan mobil Kim Hyung Soo.</font>

755
00:53:15,914 --> 00:53:17,943
<font color=#FFFF00>Tahun 2011, Kim Hyung Soo dan Hannah...</font>

756
00:53:17,943 --> 00:53:20,043
<font color=#FFFF00>terdaftar untuk rumah yang sama</font>

757
00:53:20,043 --> 00:53:21,253
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini alamatnya.</font>

758
00:53:21,784 --> 00:53:23,923
<font color=#FFFF00>Kawasan itu sedang dibangun kembali.</font>

759
00:53:24,023 --> 00:53:25,523
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat ini kosong.</font>

760
00:53:45,874 --> 00:53:47,313
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau menunggu...</font>

761
00:53:47,474 --> 00:53:49,374
<font color=#FFFF00>untuk menangkapku di sana?</font>

762
00:53:55,483 --> 00:53:56,483
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau mencari ini?</font>

763
00:53:57,124 --> 00:53:58,354
<font color=#FFFF00>Tanpa ini,</font>

764
00:53:58,784 --> 00:54:00,153
<font color=#FFFF00>kau hanya wanita lemah.</font>

765
00:54:00,824 --> 00:54:01,824
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah dirimu.</font>

766
00:54:02,293 --> 00:54:03,354
<font color=#FFFF00>Kim Hyung Soo.</font>

767
00:54:04,063 --> 00:54:06,494
<font color=#FFFF00>Begini caramu memperlakukan wanita?</font>

768
00:54:06,494 --> 00:54:08,093
<font color=#FFFF00>Agen NCI...</font>

769
00:54:09,233 --> 00:54:10,903
<font color=#FFFF00>...tidak jauh berbeda.</font>

770
00:54:11,233 --> 00:54:12,834
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang kau tahu?</font>

771
00:54:14,733 --> 00:54:17,403
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tak boleh mengenal aku.</font>

772
00:54:17,604 --> 00:54:18,744
<font color=#FFFF00>Begitu kau mengenalku,</font>

773
00:54:19,104 --> 00:54:21,144
<font color=#FFFF00>kau akan berubah pikiran.</font>

774
00:54:22,343 --> 00:54:24,414
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau sadar betapa mereka menginginkan aku...</font>

775
00:54:24,414 --> 00:54:26,313
<font color=#FFFF00>dan menyukaiku,</font>

776
00:54:28,284 --> 00:54:32,084
<font color=#FFFF00>kau akan sangat ingin mengandung anakku.</font>

777
00:54:32,584 --> 00:54:33,584
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

778
00:54:33,923 --> 00:54:35,894
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tahu betul orang macam apa kau itu.</font>

779
00:54:36,193 --> 00:54:38,963
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tak pernah mengencani wanita dengan benar.</font>

780
00:54:39,523 --> 00:54:41,894
<font color=#FFFF00>Yang kau lakukan itu mencoba mengalahkan mereka.</font>

781
00:54:43,133 --> 00:54:44,503
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau tidak mengasari mereka,</font>

782
00:54:44,503 --> 00:54:47,604
<font color=#FFFF00>kau tak bisa merasakan apa-apa.
Kau itu cabul dan sadis.</font>

783
00:54:48,204 --> 00:54:49,604
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah dirimu.</font>

784
00:54:50,343 --> 00:54:52,843
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mungkin sama mengerikannya saat masih muda.</font>

785
00:54:54,014 --> 00:54:56,173
<font color=#FFFF00>Seseorang dengan masa lalu yang baik...</font>

786
00:54:56,773 --> 00:54:58,713
<font color=#FFFF00>takkan memperlakukan wanita sepertimu.</font>

787
00:55:01,354 --> 00:55:04,653
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi kau sangat mengenalku, kan?</font>

788
00:55:06,124 --> 00:55:08,293
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisa kita periksa?</font>

789
00:55:09,324 --> 00:55:12,293
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari kita lihat betapa berbedanya
kau dibandingkan wanita lain.</font>

790
00:55:16,233 --> 00:55:18,534
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana rasanya?
Terasa nyata sekarang?</font>

791
00:55:19,164 --> 00:55:20,474
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisa kita periksa?</font>

792
00:55:22,403 --> 00:55:24,943
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak ada wanita yang pernah menatapku seperti kau.</font>

793
00:55:25,474 --> 00:55:26,604
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini menggairahkan.</font>

794
00:55:28,043 --> 00:55:29,113
<font color=#FFFF00>Diam!</font>

795
00:55:30,074 --> 00:55:31,943
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan merasa lebih baik.</font>

796
00:55:33,784 --> 00:55:35,113
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bilang, diam.</font>

797
00:55:35,113 --> 00:55:36,914
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah kubilang, ini akan lebih baik.</font>

798
00:55:57,644 --> 00:55:59,144
<font color=#FFFF00>Biar kutanyakan satu hal.</font>

799
00:56:01,074 --> 00:56:03,914
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa orang sepertimu ingin seorang anak?</font>

800
00:56:03,914 --> 00:56:04,983
<font color=#FFFF00>Lihat?</font>

801
00:56:06,914 --> 00:56:09,514
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau juga ingin mengenalku, kan?</font>

802
00:56:10,153 --> 00:56:11,784
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau suka, tapi pura-pura tidak suka.</font>

803
00:56:12,784 --> 00:56:14,454
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau 'bertindak bersih', tapi kau kotor.</font>

804
00:56:15,224 --> 00:56:16,994
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pura-pura suci padahal tidak.</font>

805
00:56:16,994 --> 00:56:18,363
<font color=#FFFF00>Kemari.</font>

806
00:56:18,363 --> 00:56:19,994
<font color=#FFFF00>- Tidak.
- Ikut aku.</font>

807
00:56:19,994 --> 00:56:21,363
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

808
00:56:22,093 --> 00:56:23,133
<font color=#FFFF00>Masuk.</font>

809
00:56:23,534 --> 00:56:26,503
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan menangis.
Diam di sana.</font>

810
00:56:26,503 --> 00:56:29,434
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak. Tidak mau.</font>

811
00:56:29,434 --> 00:56:30,574
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu.</font>

812
00:56:31,874 --> 00:56:33,343
<font color=#FFFF00>Hentikan.</font>

813
00:56:34,613 --> 00:56:36,173
<font color=#FFFF00>Seperti itulah wanita.</font>

814
00:56:36,613 --> 00:56:39,684
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hanya melayani wanita-wanita itu.</font>

815
00:56:40,514 --> 00:56:42,014
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hanya mencoba...</font>

816
00:56:43,313 --> 00:56:46,023
<font color=#FFFF00>...membuat mereka memiliki anak seperti aku.</font>

817
00:56:47,954 --> 00:56:50,593
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey, apa yang kau lakukan?</font>

818
00:56:51,363 --> 00:56:52,894
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita harus mulai lagi.</font>

819
00:57:01,574 --> 00:57:02,604
<font color=#FFFF00>Berhenti.</font>

820
00:57:02,704 --> 00:57:05,574
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?
Kau juga suka.</font>

821
00:57:07,773 --> 00:57:08,974
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini yang kau mau?</font>

822
00:57:11,084 --> 00:57:14,713
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau mau berakhir seperti yang ada di TV atau...</font>

823
00:57:54,693 --> 00:57:58,394
<font color=#FFFF00>"Tragedi adalah alat bagi yang hidup
untuk mendapatkan kebijaksanaan,"</font>

824
00:57:58,764 --> 00:58:01,994
<font color=#FFFF00>"...bukan panduan untuk hidup."</font>

825
00:58:02,563 --> 00:58:03,804
<font color=#FFFF00>Robert Kennedy.</font>

